<%= render :partial => 'layouts/opportunities' %>

<div class="wrapper">
  <div class="content-container">

    <div class="main-content">
      <h2>Share a Reflection</h2>
      <p>A reflection is your recap on the state of this opportunity after action was taken.  Were things improved?  Was the action successful?  Would you recommend doing it again?  Etcâ€¦</p>
      
      <form></form>
      <fieldset class="form-group">
      <label for="conversation_title">Title:</label>
      <input id="conversation_title" name="conversation[title]" size="30" type="text" />
      </fieldset>
      
      <div id='contribution_tool_container'>
        <label for="conversation_title">Your Reflection:</label>
              <div id="contrib" name="contrib" class="contrib_tool_container">
                <form accept-charset="UTF-8" class="contribution_new" data-remote="true" enctype="multipart/form-data" id="contribution_new" method="post">
                  <fieldset>
                    <textarea class="content" cols="40" id="contribution_content" name="contribution[content]" rows="20"></textarea>
                  </fieldset>
                  <fieldset class="button-group">
                    <input class="submit" id="contribution_submit" name="commit" type="submit" value="Publish" /> or 
                    <a href="#" id="cancel-contribution">Cancel</a>
                  </fieldset>
              </form>
            </div>
        </div>
            
    </div><!-- /.main-content -->

    <div class='aside supplementary'>
      <p>You participated in the following actions, would you like to reference them in your reflection?</p>
      <hr />
      <p>Petition Cedar Fair to turn SeaWorld into a whale breeding motel.</p>
    </div><!-- /.aside -->

  </div>
</div>